{"tid":874920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港豬噢] 熊永達認為香港應跟內地轉左駄　林鄭任內需處理","createTime":"2018-10-24T14:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T05:50:30.000Z","uid":51620,"like":9,"dislike":421,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bd75641c531bfd3a716b46f56160047dd821ec","tid":874920,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/261870/%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E7%86%8A%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%94%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E8%B7%9F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%BD%89%E5%B7%A6%E9%A7%84%e3%80%80/?fbclid=IwAR1hj8UeSLFVV3yCWcHT8nFt4--JJks2tAhyN4mREt9yCm5cnR2SwMYPIZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F261870%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2586%258A%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25B7%259F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E9%25A7%2584%25e3%2580%2580%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1hj8UeSLFVV3yCWcHT8nFt4--JJks2tAhyN4mREt9yCm5cnR2SwMYPIZA&d=3l%2FvdMGQVhuJuhsOpjTboW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=87e2ee33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/261870/%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E7%86%8A%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%94%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E8%B7%9F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%BD%89%E5%B7%A6%E9%A7%84%e3%80%80/?fbclid=IwAR1hj8UeSLFVV3yCWcHT8nFt4--JJks2tAhyN4mREt9yCm5cnR2SwMYPIZA</a><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋昨日舉行開通儀式，香港運輸研究學會資深會員熊永達今日出席電台節目後向傳媒表示，香港應考慮改變行車方式，跟隨內地使用左駄。<br />\n<br />\n熊永達指，內地車輛的司機位在左邊，而香港是在右邊，兩地的駕駛習慣不同，如果路上有大量混合的駕駛方式，將會有很大風險。他認為香港可能要考慮改變駕駛方式，但不肯定需時多長。<br />\n<br />\n熊永達表示，暫時未見政府內有人考慮處理這事情，但這應該是特首林鄭月娥應該處理的事，長遠以言很難想像全國都使用左駄時，香港仍保持右駄。"},{"pid":"d734fe50463e64d1a92c8a555a567bf9d458d2ad","tid":874920,"uid":351,"like":217,"dislike":1,"score":216,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:31:13.