-10-24T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/874656/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/874656/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n愛國愛黨肥閪排頭位等&quot;港豬噢大橋&quot;開通"},{"pid":"c82b46eea24f555b3e6ceb6ed49871012d72f00f","tid":874920,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c03adb660cd31a31869db601ab0ca9766cf5ee59","tid":874920,"uid":192813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"為咗擦鞋可以去到幾盡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"係鞋油問題<br />\n係租界歷史, 二戰後民國時代統一同訂立全部左駄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd022d246eb7212b5519cea2eba5d03c3645691","tid":874920,"uid":23873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"熊永達 －民主黨成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c4d8b5db8ca488c396dfda007cb28c4cd95334","tid":874920,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"一改都唔知改幾耐，on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4678b60ad7190d8d75611d6bb21a313425d45c","tid":874920,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74b615513714fe413bad1c96bdb48facf0c92d2","tid":874920,"uid":23873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cbd022d246eb7212b5519cea2eba5d03c3645691","tid":874920,"uid":23873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"熊永達 －民主黨成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"【689四周年】當年提名CY泛民熊永達擬不再當選委<br />\n<br />\n上屆特首選舉，梁振英的提名名單中亦有少數泛民選委，包括民主黨黨員、高等教育界選委熊永達。熊指，當時泛民何俊仁已夠票入閘，形勢上另一候選人唐英年又幾乎篤定當選，為鼓勵選舉真正有得鬥，便選擇提名告急的梁振英。現實上，梁入閘也促成唐梁二人互揭瘡疤的激烈競爭，不過他強調「我絕對冇投票畀梁振英」。<br />\n<br />\n熊永達說，中央對選委會的設計花盡心思，若非阿爺心水的候選人，縱使夠票入閘，也絕無勝算。他指，作為少數有自由意志選委，當時決定提名的想法相當簡單，「想真係有得跑吓，到投票嘅時候又會唔同，咪畀機會佢（梁振英）跑吓」。往後情節市民或許印象猶深，唐、梁二人相繼被揭僭建，梁更在論壇中，被唐踢爆要以防暴隊對付示威者，「雖然有冇我提名票都差唔多，但真係多咗好多激辯競爭機會」。<br />\n<br />\n對於過去4年梁班子施政，熊永達形容，情況與回歸後歷屆政府相同，「只懂有火撲火」，在熊熟悉的交通運輸政策更不見新猶。熊連任高教界選委多年，對於選委的作用受限，他亦感意興闌珊，打算趁即將退休不再角逐選委。當日有份提名梁振英的泛民人士，包括公民黨吳永順、教育界周慧珍、衞生服務界周昭賢，及屬泛民友好的宗教界毛祺昌等。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160323/54902148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160323%2F54902148&d=3l%2FvdMGQVhuJuhsOpjTboW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=4c012e1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160323%2F54902148&h=05b32a81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160323/54902148</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9ccdc1bbb9d153af2fc8dcecd7fd5ac954d7ce","tid":874920,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d27d64334b3cb30d781f51b5326438f3c7f954d","tid":874920,"uid":51937,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"起呢條大橋嘅作用就係為改變呢個習慣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"d大陸狗真係咁想法 話支那同美國都係超級大國都係左<br />\n仲係右都係垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ec82094cbb0614b7b9382b2c263119275519e8","tid":874920,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"on9仔一名死撚柒左佢喇，屌你老母個閪！"},{"pid":"458831682d3d2b5ed8e97cd2f34eac7f4598f85a","tid":874920,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd022d246eb7212b5519cea2eba5d03c3645691","tid":874920,"uid":23873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"熊永達 －民主黨成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-