你，他要做檢討！」他表示會經 ..."},{"pid":"8a1f008cd056dc4ba73607b95c4461364fcedb0c","tid":874920,"uid":22622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"從源頭消除風險，一架左馱車都唔俾進入香港境內咪得囉"},{"pid":"6229fe042fb7ec0d077858a05ca678a2a0d25961","tid":874920,"uid":351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d6383e2eb2813d2058d5b41f4ee7a0d0f9738f4","tid":874920,"uid":88461,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6857dc3d23c26e4b8d91434e5f950a0345fa92c9","tid":874920,"uid":149496,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"quote":{"pid":"d734fe50463e64d1a92c8a555a567bf9d458d2ad","tid":874920,"uid":351,"like":217,"dislike":1,"score":216,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢以為換哂車將兩邊線掉轉就得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"我記得top gear有集去左緬甸定唔知越南<br />\n<br />\n話咩以前行開左駄 個政府話覺得太左 (左翼) 所以兩邊調轉 搞到啲人揸車on99<br />\n<br />\n巴士落車唔係落係行人路邊 係落係大馬路嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz4DhDJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz4DhDJ.png&h=a9783d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDrive on the right side<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T18:44:41.000Z","msg":"正確嘅事要由小事開始<br />\nSit on the right side of the car"},{"pid":"7399bf101e6b9eda7b09d659247fc63994603be0","tid":874920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T23:39:20.000Z","msg":"行車線要配合改為右上左落<br />\n好似商場迎合自由行支那人<br />\n電梯改為右上左落一樣"},{"pid":"604b299f2c1e334a48b4f5e67582362f017ccb6a","tid":874920,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim